erate transmission of hiv aids  ',0),(1920,'node',' other  other right to exploit natural wealth resources attempted murder  ',0),(1921,'node',' test22  in process human rights violation region a  ',0),(1922,'node',' atim e  awaiting trial human rights violation  ',0);
